WEBVTT

00:05:00.760 --> 00:05:02.936
Now, I believed in art therapy,

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:05.976
but I was going to have
to convince service members,

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:09.736
big, tough, strong, manly military men,

00:05:09.760 --> 00:05:11.496
and some women too,

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:15.520
to give art-making as
a psychotherapeutic intervention a try.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:20.520
The results have been
nothing short of spectacular.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:24.376
Vivid, symbolic artwork

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:27.376
is being created
by our servicemen and women,

00:05:27.400 --> 00:05:29.920
and every work of art tells a story.